        business - describe a business object that this coupon belongs
        couponName - describe Coupon Name ,Updating the table column couponName
        image - describe Coupon image by URL of coupon image,save to file, and Updating the table column image
        detail - describe all detail of a Coupon ,Updating the table column detail
        price - describe a Coupon price sell,Updating the table column price
        lastDate - describe a Coupon Offer valid if the date smaller then today date
        category - describe a category object that this coupon belongs
        expire - boolean variable describe if a coupon expire or not .
        latitude - it describe Coupon latitude point in a Coupon table ,Updating the table column latitude
        longitude - it describe Coupon longitude point in a Coupon table ,Updating the table column longitude
